author: Mary
title: Mary
text: American Frame is my "go to" company for both my professional business (photographer) and my personal framing needs. They have a great selection, their customer service is extremely attentive, shipping is so careful (everything arrives perfectly), and pricing is competitive. They're SO reliable - I've trusted them to give me the best frames and value for my exhibitions!
